## Dual-Hand Support Implementation
```python
def analyze_dual_hand(data):
    left_hand_data = data[data['hand'] == 'left']
    right_hand_data = data[data['hand'] == 'right']

    # Analyzing both hands
    process_hand_data(left_hand_data)
    process_hand_data(right_hand_data)
```

## Advanced Biomechanics Metrics
```python
def calculate_metrics(data):
    # New advanced metrics for biomechanics
    metrics = {"velocity": np.mean(data['velocity']),
               "acceleration": np.mean(data['acceleration']),
               "force": np.mean(data['force'])}
    return metrics
```

## Data Export Functionality
```python
def export_to_csv(data, file_name):
    data.to_csv(file_name, index=False)
    print(f'Data exported to {file_name}')
```

## Main Analysis Function
```python
if __name__ == '__main__':
    data = load_data('biomechanics_data.csv')
